title: 860. Big Week 2 Games, 8 Biggest Questions, Standout Rookies & Favorite Performances
itunes:title: 860. Big Week 2 Games, 8 Biggest Questions, Standout Rookies & Favorite Performances
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and all the action from Week 2 of the NFL season. The guys start by breaking down the big 3 games from Sunday. Next, the group answer their 8 biggest questions after Week 2. After that, the trio each give a standout rookie and also their favorite performance in Week 2. Then, the guys recap the Buccaneers vs Saints rivalry game. To wrap up the show, the trio hit on a few takeaways from the college football weekend.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
